Sets a value in a nested dictionary structure, creating intermediate dictionaries as needed.
Sample usage:

  d = {}
  safe_set(d, "a", "b", "c", value=42)

d is now:
  {
    "a": {
      "b": {
        "c": 42
      }
    }
  }

